let's make a game!
name: Dragon Empire
author: Fenicf0x 
desc: <b>Rise from humble hatchling to <t>Dragon Lord</t>!</b><br/><q>Command lairs, hoard gold, and crush kingdoms!<//><.>Dynamic <b>text effects</b><.>Advanced <u>production chains</u><.>Complex <g#f90>upgrades</g#></q>
version: 2.0
created: 04/02/2026
updated: 04/02/2026

Settings
stylesheet: stuff/bigBlue.css
building cost increase: 118%
spritesheet: icons, 48 by 48, https://orteil.dashnet.org/igm/stuff/icons.png

Resources
*gold
  name: <b>[n:this]</b> [<g#f90>[this]</g#>] 
  desc: <b>Dragon hoard currency</b><.>Used for everything.<.>[?(this>=10000|<i>Poor</i>|<i>RICH!</i>)]
  icon: icons[0,0]

*eggs
  name: Dragon Eggs
  desc: <q>Freshly laid. Need warmth to hatch.</q>
  icon: icons[1,0]

*wyrmlings
  name: Wyrmlings
  desc: <b>Baby dragons</b> - cute but deadly!
  icon: icons[2,0]

*fire
  name: Dragonfire
  desc: <#ff4400>Scorching heat</> from dragon breath.
  icon: icons[3,0]

*essence
  name: Draconic Essence
  desc: <#aa00ff>Concentrated dragon power</>.
  icon: icons[4,0]

Buttons
*hunt
  name: <t>HUNT</t>
  desc: Send dragons to raid villages. Gain <g#f90>[random(1,5)] gold</g#>.
  icon: icons[5,0]
  class: bigButton hasFlares
  on click:
    $loot=random(1,5)
    if (have raiders) $loot=$loot*2
    yield $loot gold
    if (chance(10%)) yield 1 eggs
  end
  text: <b>Raid!</b> <i>Click for gold</i>

*incubate
  name: Incubate Eggs
  desc: Warm eggs with dragonfire to hatch wyrmlings.
  icon: icons[1,0]
  req: fire 10
  cost: 5 eggs, 10 fire
  on click: yield 2 wyrmlings

Buildings
*lair
  name: Dragon Lair
  desc: <#f90>Warm cave</> where eggs safely hatch.<.>Produces <b>wyrmlings</b>.
  icon: icons[6,0]
  cost: 50 gold
  on tick: yield 0.1 eggs, 0.05 wyrmlings

*flamePit
  name: Flame Pit
  desc: <#ff4400>Roaring fire pit</> generates heat.<.>Boosts lair hatching.
  icon: icons[3,0]
  cost: 200 gold, 10 eggs
  req: lair 2
  on tick: yield 1 fire

*hoardVault
  name: Hoard Vault
  desc: <b>Impregnable vault</b> protects gold production.
  icon: icons[0,0]
  cost: 1000 gold, 20 wyrmlings
  req: flamePit 3
  on tick: yield 2 gold

*essenceAltar
  name: Essence Altar
  desc: <#aa00ff>Extracts pure essence</> from sacrifices.
  icon: icons[4,0]
  cost: 5000 gold, 50 wyrmlings, 100 fire
  req: hoardVault 5
  on tick: yield 0.02 essence

*wyrmRider
  name: Wyrm Rider Squadron
  desc: <i>Elite dragon cavalry</i> raids distant kingdoms.
  icon: icons[2,0]
  cost: 25000 gold, 200 wyrmlings, 10 essence
  req: essenceAltar 3
  on tick: yield 15 gold

*ancientLair
  name: Ancient Lair
  desc: <#f0f><t>Boosts ALL production 2x</t></>.
  icon: icons[7,0]
  cost: 100000 gold, 1000 wyrmlings, 500 fire, 50 essence
  req: wyrmRider 10
  passive: multiply yield of :Buildings by 2

Upgrades
*reinforcedLairs
  name: Reinforced Lairs
  desc: <b>Lairs produce 50% more eggs.</b>
  icon: icons[6,0]
  cost: 750 gold
  req: lair 10
  passive: multiply eggs yield of lair by 1.5

*fireproofEggs
  name: Fireproof Eggs
  desc: Eggs need <#ff4400>less fire</> to hatch.
  icon: icons[1,0]
  cost: 1500 gold, 50 fire
  req: flamePit 5
  passive: multiply cost of incubate fire by 0.5

*dragonTrainers
  name: Dragon Trainers
  desc: <i>Wyrmlings grow 2x faster.</i>
  icon: icons[2,0]
  cost: 4000 gold, 100 wyrmlings
  passive: multiply wyrmlings yield of lair by 2

*essenceRitual
  name: Essence Ritual
  desc: <#aa00ff>Double essence production.</>
  icon: icons[4,0]
  cost: 20000 gold, 20 essence
  req: essence 20
  passive: multiply essence yield of essenceAltar by 2

*raidMasters
  name: Raid Masters
  desc: <b>Hunting yields [huntLoot*2] gold!</b>
  icon: icons[5,0]
  cost: 50000 gold
  passive:
    $huntLoot=2
    increase gold yield of hunt by $huntLoot
  end

